{"type": "article", "id": 51589, "title": "陈冠希的“一只猴子”快闪店要来上海，以及，上海时装周开幕 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-03-29T04:05:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}, {"id": 17411, "name": "陈冠希"}, {"id": 3321, "name": "Stella McCartney"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 33975, "name": "Anti Social Social Club"}, {"id": 2120, "name": "开云"}, {"id": 25410, "name": "PVH"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180329110906p05jAVnxB8vCh2rD.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Calvin-Klein-Tommy-Hilfiger-lead-PVH-Corp-to-record-revenue-year,963027.html#.WrxOoNNub-Y\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>受 Calvin Klein、Tommy Hilfiger 业绩推动，PVH 集团表现好于预期</strong></a> | PVH 集团日前发布财报称，去年全年录得 89 亿美元的收入，增长 9％，净收入下降了 2%，为 5.378 亿美元。集团 CEO 表示，对去年的表现感到满意，由于旗下品牌 Tommy Hilfiger 和 Calvin Klein 业务发展势头强劲，业绩增长超过了长期目标。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/exclusive-why-stella-mccartney-take-full-control-brand-buying-kering-1202639973/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Stella McCartney 正式收回同名品牌股权</strong></a> | 周三，开云集团同意向 Stella McCartney 品牌创始人出售 50% 的股权，这意味着在 Stella McCartney 与开云从 2010 年开始合作之后，Stella McCartney 完全控制同名品牌。Stella McCartney 本人称，为何离开开云是一个“很难回答的问题”，但双方承诺将实现平稳过渡，Stella McCartney 将以品牌代表的可持续时尚与开云继续合作。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>adidas 邀请了以 Kendall Jenner 为首的五位女性创作者来演绎全新鞋款<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/adidas-arkyn-sneaker/#slide-19\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Arkyn</a>，这双鞋款将于 4 月 5 日全球发售，宣传片拍的很生活化。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111705b9karJL1nR6NBOIC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803291117067BPAJc9toUr4LVCu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111708GxhTw7DpeqkfYsPc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111709v85YDCcuxIshQNOo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111710WQo64HJBG1AzxyO2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498829\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111713Vez18RM3OTHI6tF9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111713SojA2ZPta93LIUlE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111719uYBWvxiadVZC3Sln.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111719BgPCMKtk0bjS5rc1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111721fVHbUrvyASaZLidY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018032911172341RdHXw8l0QbiE7y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111725He6qZGXr2JjfRSyP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111726tKlSL1ksIa7jFNAm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111726RXMybr8cTFOQxKL4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111726ysfZCKG6wEnctdgQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111727EVce2LJPbG0U8Irx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111728auHR9x1IcCYLPB0W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/anti-social-social-club-neighborhood-japan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anti Social Social Club 和 Neighborhood 合作推出联名系列</a>，该系列包括棒球外套、扇子和眼镜蛇的小摆件，将于 3 月 31 日率先登陆 Neighborhood 在东京的快闪店“The Answer”，随后登陆日本、美国、韩国的各大旗舰店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111644DK0Hm7nUZXt6pLrC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111646GrJ3Z5oV2maOqH1Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803291116459dE2C7p3ZaoPKXxO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111646gfZqAeLYkCp8X70r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111646N8K3jCRVSckmW7ix.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111646WuRTriLcmfU9gaCO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>4 月 1 日至 15 日，继去年在北京尤伦斯举办一只猴子“音术”展之后，陈冠希将来到上海开设<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2018/3/edison-little-monkey-pop-up-store\" rel=\"nofollow\">一只猴子</a>快闪店，带来多款服饰单品以及和 New Era 的合作帽款，地址是上海市虹口区瑞虹路 188 号月亮湾 5 楼月光露台。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111041PUftLD6vASJHc5zQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.765000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111035jrp89VBfyIG4lk6t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803291110352yP3fzlABTN6RMpj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036moGhYzqyVx7u3M0g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111035sHO62ljfQBR9ZKmc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667888\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111035D1mz0o3kwZMrcRvJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667888\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111035lMxqDSQwKRo6Hafn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667888\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036ej7iXvH3bhAxd6po.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036qaAFNT0mXDWrBCSu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036wBoavPzpiIStEljn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036bHj3IFPEBmivkAKJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036bAzTdJWBFEcuLHDr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111036gZhj2rELeB57MSC1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037OW9S1TEkXqBPerm7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037j83DXqwF2ESaQ4bu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037QHJSVgIMni67xb0A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037fMZgpFLAdiEK5m6G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037WM0NwXuanHp4Bz7A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803291110378kyo79qt6M3DOeAd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037LvjU1JoPhDKqt4Rw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111037zFYyOIiPAv8uLshT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018032911103775b19LyJfTOn6rDF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111038XvxwygoFL1jf8420.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329111038o18gdTyUtfeRnFDa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>3 月 28 日，上海时装周正式开幕，在新天地主秀场，一共有 PRONOUNCE、JUNNE、HAIZHENWANG、Disney、deepmoss、C.J.YAO、ANIRAC 这七个品牌走秀。我们从中挑选了部分：&nbsp;</p><p><strong>PRONOUNCE</strong></p><p>《智族 GQ》与男装品牌 PRONOUNCE 再度合作，发布“INFINITY ∞ ”主题系列首秀。 </p><p>PRONOUNCE 成立于 2016 年，以实用主义著称。这一季中，可以看到李雨山、周俊这两位设计师把传统西方立体剪裁技巧与东方审美的结合，比如用灵感来自中式梅花扣、形似“∞”的曲线环扣代替传统男士西装中的牛角扣，对中山装的全新诠释。同时，品牌使用了多种面料，比如防皱羊毛面料、皮、帆布与 T P U 等面料的穿插使用，还有一款自主研发漆皮效果的羊毛覆膜面料。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112302C2X8JDiAsL6GPFqv.png\" data-ratio=\"0.743875\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112237j6n5dke9mypNui4W.png\" data-ratio=\"1.509009\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112242Ym2DQkBgheHXCG0Z.png\" data-ratio=\"1.504484\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112243Zcr5EhvTgDijmMsU.png\" data-ratio=\"1.506757\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112243Ric5VHs8UOyawbj6.png\" data-ratio=\"1.509009\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112243EcqP4jtJHi2N8rTS.png\" data-ratio=\"1.512415\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112243t3cHU0NB6SWTDZnj.png\" data-ratio=\"1.505618\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112247kX1AoMyj03hvRY2n.png\" data-ratio=\"1.510112\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112248IpjO4tA8n2TviRCr.png\" data-ratio=\"1.504505\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112249V2xfCFatNmPvJcDp.png\" data-ratio=\"1.515695\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112250shodP4mzCZfENxI8.png\" data-ratio=\"1.512415\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112250LDXU30iBsCEjrRez.png\" data-ratio=\"1.515837\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018032911225079iedAUhDl6Rzmwn.png\" data-ratio=\"1.508969\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112253pNayrcBnbZqsVioR.png\" data-ratio=\"1.509050\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112254jTdsfSvGrhHxE6UP.png\" data-ratio=\"1.506757\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112256fYE8RrCGeFW3ZqH1.png\" data-ratio=\"1.504505\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112257CHgB3WLbuNKaZmwT.png\" data-ratio=\"1.510158\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112258nrJBtTLv7pxQjPV3.png\" data-ratio=\"1.506787\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112259Mhsd2A17gKcRIDqL.png\" data-ratio=\"1.503371\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112259MhZNIOVvSY0sCw1z.png\" data-ratio=\"1.514607\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112300ipTtSg3oXDwYeq6H.png\" data-ratio=\"1.507865\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112302iOVt2gIebLsF6HaY.png\" data-ratio=\"1.515837\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong>HAIZHENWANG</strong></p><p>设计师王海震的品牌 HAIZHENWANG 2018秋冬系列作品以“Revived 复兴”为题，灵感来自中世纪欧洲庄园仕女衣著，包含乡村与宫廷画案等古典元素。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112957qo9eOLsB0gQUTWXS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113031i6QGOvAacof2U0jk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112928PYhpvb5dCfgktZFV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112929owl4a3QcHWOJSZ9Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112929tDfcSzu03IH6dJNE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112933mI7GZEfVWQUFsMdl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112943rQc9tkWpfSF7XIYZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329112954FOr1hpANuK2a097s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113001svYZNygM5HaneEkl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113008VCYiEaLD8NwRTIO4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113013MX3FaOHnf0wtWeTZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113017IAPZrV4SNsaCpQvb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113024JlAv8KMq4HzOWmQR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113024RDexa1QEPYA8ocd0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113027pIYQjw4aSLJrdCb2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113027C6mJQF3e87gpnZG4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>deepmoss </strong></p><p>deepmoss 是设计师刘小路创办于 2013 年的品牌。2018 秋冬系列以艺术家路易斯·布尔乔亚的作品为灵感，初次尝试用皮革结合金属与机能性面料，试图用廓形表达能量感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803291132055b8rKazluqMQPc7t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113211WNTez6prLmhElXd7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113215u9Tk5NZhFtQdwi81.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113222ByN7ZnlQ9pcGWuLz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113224lpVQ9nsWetMjfFw1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113230lGjZ7K8IW3a6e9fb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113235CeHUaixZSM2zFEou.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113235vJXHxt9wCIQEYAz5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803291132384Ut8AsFcuWTyVbjv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113243xThNbDu2I1aH6yli.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113243cg3o6RdjNXPWiOKA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113246TVxNYWdaG0oPD4q2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018032911324714u0Ao3ZBsSOh2L8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113249eTus1oPWBcz0l4jK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180329113253hNlZMRmYwuFI58DT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：HAIZHENWANG</p>"}